# This repo tracks ONLY the Claude review tooling + settings (.claude/).
# Everything else in the project is ignored.

# --- Ignore everything by default ---
/*

# --- ...then re-include just what we want to track ---
!.gitignore
!.claude/
!README.md
!LICENSE
!NOTICE

# --- Within .claude/, exclude heavy / generated / transient bits ---
# Vendored dependencies (reinstall from manifests: composer.json / package.json)
.claude/review/tools/vendor/
.claude/review/tools/node_modules/

# Transient review runtime state + logs
.claude/.review-state/
.claude/review/**/*.log

# Local/secret settings (keep shared settings.json; ignore personal overrides)
.claude/settings.local.json

# Upstream-feedback / critique docs — kept local, shared privately, not published
.claude/review/FEEDBACK_FOR_TDD_DEV.md
.claude/review/ADOPTER_REPORT.md
.claude/review/UPSTREAM_FEEDBACK.md
.claude/review/ADDENDUM_v2.1.md

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
